**Explaination**

Calculate weeks before given day week,
`7*((4*x) + (x*(x-1))/2)`, where x is weeks passed
which is calculated by `x=n/7`
add sum of the given week to it

**Complexity**

Time `O(1)`
Space `O(1)`

**C++ Code**

```
class Solution {
public:
    int totalMoney(int n) {
        int weekspassed = n/7;
        int givenWeekDays = n%7;
        int totalSum = 7*((4*weekspassed) + (weekspassed*(weekspassed-1))/2);
        int starting = weekspassed+1;
        for(int i=0; i<givenWeekDays; i++) {
            totalSum += starting;
            starting++;
        }
        return totalSum;
    }
};
```

